WHAT
----

gaudi effects is a set of video effect plugins for GStreamer.

list of GStreamer elements:
	- chromium
	- burn
	- dodge
	- exclusion


HOW
---

First you need to build the elements:
	./autogen.sh
	make

Then you can use the elements, for example:
    gst-launch-0.10 --gst-plugin-path=$PWD filesrc location=$some_video ! decodebin ! ffmpegcolorspace ! chromium ! ffmpegcolorspace ! xvimagesink
